-!- TISSUE SPECIFICITY: Ubiquitously expressed.
-!- SIMILARITY: Contains 1 DDT domain.
-!- SIMILARITY: Contains 1 PHD-type zinc finger.
-!- CAUTION: Ref.3 (AAG43114) sequence differs from that shown due to
    a frameshift in position 539.
-!- CAUTION: Ref.5 (BAA91591) sequence differs from that shown due to
